        "l2": "アニメなどの二次元では納得がいっても、三次元になると納得できないストーリーもありますよね。",
        "en": "In two-dimensional works like anime, there are times when you can accept it, but once it becomes three-dimensional, there are also stories you can’t accept, right?"
